Package gerberFileReader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    A class to hold Gerber attributes
    AttributeDictionary
    A class to hold a mapping of attribute names to their corresponding attributes
    GerberFileReader
    A class to read and parse Gerber files into Java objects suitable for further processing.
    GraphicalObject
    A class for representing Gerber graphical objects
    GraphicsStream
    A class to hold a stream of Gerber Graphical Objects.
    MetaData
    A class to hold data about graphics objects that isn't specified by the Gerber Layer Format Specification but nonetheless could make life much easier for someone trying to process those objects.
    RepeatCount
    A class to hold the repeat count for objects created by Gerber Step and Repeat Blocks.
    StrokeInfo
    A class to hold Java AWT Geometry stroke information for Gerber GraphicalObjects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AttributeType
    An enumeration of Gerber attribute types - FILE, APERTURE, and OBJECT
    Polarity
    An enumeration of Gerber Polarities, either DARK meaning opaque or CLEAR meaning transparent
    Units
    An enumeration of Gerber coordinate units, either INCHES or MILLIMETERS.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GerberLayerFormatException
    A class to represent various exceptions that can occur during the parsing of invalid Gerber files
